"./Lean/Meta/Sym/AlphaShareCommon.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.AlphaKey","kind":"structure","line":77,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.AlphaKey","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/AlphaShareCommon.lean#L77-L78"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/AlphaShareCommon.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.isUnfoldReducibleCandidate\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">isUnfoldReducibleCandidate</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">env</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Environment.html#Lean.Environment\">Environment</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns `true` if `declName` is a reducible constant that the `unfoldReducible`\npreprocessing step must unfold.\n\nProjection functions are excluded even though they are `reducible` by default:\nunfolding them produces kernel projections, which the `foldProjs` preprocessing\nstep folds back into projection function applications.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/AlphaShareCommon.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.isUnfoldReducibleCandidate","kind":"def","line":65,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.isUnfoldReducibleCandidate","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/AlphaShareCommon.lean#L65-L75"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/AlphaShareCommon.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.isGrindGadget\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">isGrindGadget</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns `true` if `declName` is the name of a grind helper declaration that\nshould not be unfolded by `unfoldReducible`. `Grind.EqMatch` and `Grind.MatchCond`\nare `abbrev`s, but they are gadgets that must survive until the corresponding\npropagators consume them.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/AlphaShareCommon.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.isGrindGadget","kind":"def","line":56,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.isGrindGadget","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/AlphaShareCommon.lean#L56-L63"}}],"imports":["Init.Grind.Util","Lean.Environment","Lean.Meta.Sym.ExprPtr","Lean.ProjFns","Lean.ReducibilityAttrs"],"instances":[{"className":"Hashable","name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.instHashableAlphaKey","typeNames":["Lean.Meta.Sym.AlphaKey"]},{"className":"BEq","name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.instBEqAlphaKey","typeNames":["Lean.Meta.Sym.AlphaKey"]}],"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.AlphaShareCommon"}